    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chroma Cross</strong> is a game about <i>Picross / Nonongram</i> puzzles with the refreshing twist of more than binary black and white colors. The usual <i>Picross</i> rules apply, but now the clue’s color needs to be considered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080030/extras/a38c0436cf450eec7d36a749a81e3fd8.poster.avif?t=1771780967\" width=524 height=504 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080030/extras/a38c0436cf450eec7d36a749a81e3fd8.webm?t=1771780967\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080030/extras/a38c0436cf450eec7d36a749a81e3fd8.mp4?t=1771780967\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play puzzles in all manner of sizes, from 5x5 to even 25x25 and beyond. Enjoy a variety of themes such as Food, Plants, Spooky and more.</p>",
